  <brief_title>FOLFOX-4 3months Versus 6 Months and Bevacizumab as Adjuvant Therapy for Patients With Stage II/III Colon Cancer</brief_title>
  <acronym>TOSCA</acronym>
  <official_title>A Randomized Trial Investigating the Role of FOLFOX-4 Regimen Duration (3 Versus 6 Months) and Bevacizumab as Adjuvant Therapy for Patients With Stage II/III Colon Cancer</official_title>
